{"tid":2036941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5/27  是伏! (入黎睇一睇或者鬧下都好)","createTime":"2020-05-26T18:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T18:24:41.000Z","uid":359312,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"421f37500242de0ab1f05e5dab2fe35aaf542b9a","tid":2036941,"uid":359312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:07:10.000Z","msg":"以下幾點覺得5/27 伏味濃, 大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n(1) 5/27出黎, 5/27高中復課<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔番學姐係代表咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日期一早SET好哂<br />\n<br />\n(2) 5/27 只是國歌法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5/24 兩會討論國安法, 有原因要出黎行街街<br />\n不過5/27 只是二讀國歌法, 嚴重程度差太遠<br />\n如果要出, 點解唔星期四人大表決先出?<br />\n讓對家 &quot;一鼓作氣, 再而衰, 三而歇&quot; (BE WATER)<br />\n<br />\n(3) 人少 = 送頭<br />\n5/24 係星期日假期, 都甘少人 (封唔到路, 由得駕水炮來來回回走)<br />\n5/27 仲要番工, 你估下會唔會有5/24既人數 (勇武好珍貴, 每次捉100仲有幾多個)<br />\n身邊D朋友之前會出, 呢兩次因為限聚令都通通唔出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最壞情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期四表決通過佐, 都仲有幾個月先會實施條法例。 <br />\n幾個月限聚令點都完啦, 選一個假期先和平遊行, 向世界表達香港人既意願啦 (再黎一個二百萬THANKS)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(4) 最重要係美帝已經好大聲話星期四如果通過, 會有強烈反應<br />\n英國都講明國安法係摧毀中英聯明聲明, 會收留BNO持有人<br />\n暫時國際就國安法既關注已經足夠, 不需要5/27再用流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />引起外界關注<br />\n<br />\n(5) 如果國安法表決前有激烈畫面, 更加比到位對家大造文章。<br />\n把我地打成&quot;恐怖主義&quot;, 大條道理推國安法維護國家安全<br />\n(話不定又會有演員出黎擲汽油彈)<br />\n<br />\n小小意見, 以上幾點大家都知, 我大擔推測下。 目的都係唔想見到無謂既犧牲。<br />\n參考佐沈旭輝既文章, 大家可以睇睇 (少少長, 不過分析得好好): <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3290557454311715/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F3290557454311715%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=d3f49270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3290557454311715/</a><br />\n<br />\n預佐俾人罵放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d866e78392d59d0ca599a0f3618548c2723cd30","tid":2036941,"uid":359312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:10:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31b5feeeec899c180be8461e2c4606417aa65a9a","tid":2036941,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:14:25.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"9bf5962ca096a76ee9fd4a79d13629154df9bf3e","tid":2036941,"uid":186521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:14:32.000Z","msg":"同意 28重要啲"},{"pid":"0f67e986791a1252a11f196bacff4af494a434f1","tid":2036941,"uid":115988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:15:42.000Z","msg":"【527金鐘？】每次盲目複製成功抗爭經驗，都慘敗收場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036949</a>"},{"pid":"08854b05cca1467f2868d7537676fb995e002f46","tid":2036941,"uid":180977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:24:41.000Z","msg":"合理"}]}